                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 3r: Note on the content of the codex.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 3r: ዝውእቱ፡ ነገረ፡ ሕማማቲሁ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ውእቱ፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 87v: Scribe's rhymed note on the completing of the work, extended with a supplication for ˀabunä ˁArˀaya Śəllase. </locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 87v: ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አምላኩ፡ ለዮሐንስ። ዘአፈጸመኒ፡ እንበለ፡ ደዌ፡ ዘሥጋ፡ ወነፍስ። ወይዕቀበነ፡ ለኵልነ፡ እመከራሁ፡ ለዲያብሎስ። ወፈድፋደሰ፡ ለአቡነ፡ አርዓያ፡ ሥላሴ፡…</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 176v (below): Donation note.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 176v (below): ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘሓንታ፡ ሐጐስ፡ ሃፍተ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ዘተጽሕፈ፡ በ፲፻ወ፰፻፺ወ፫ቱ፡ አመተ፡ መሕረት፡ ዘወሐቦ፡ ለታቦተ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ በለሳ፡ ዘተሐንፀ፡ በዘመነ፡ መንግሥቱ፡ ለስሑል፡ ሚካኤል፡ ወስመ፡ ጥምቀቱ፡ ተወልደ፡ መድሕን፡ ወአቡኁ፡ ኀብተ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ወውሉዱ፡ መዝገበ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ገብረ፡ መድሕን፡...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Excerpts from hymns for the Good Friday (?) with musical notation are added in the upper margins of fols. 87v, 102v, 103r, 103v, 119v, 123v, 124r, 124v, 157v.&#xD;
- Crude notes on the margins written in blue pen in fols. 5r, 66r, 71r.&#xD;
- The scribe reduces the size of the script in text with musical notation, e.g., on fols. 9vc, 10rc, 10vb, 11ra, 11rc.  &#xD;
- Minor notes, writing excercises on fols. 1r, 1v, 2r, 2v, 2ar, 176v.</item>
                     </list>
