               <person instant="false"><!--donor-->
                  <persName corresp="PRS0000" instant="false" full="yes">Ḥagwäs Haftä (Habtä) Mikaʾel whose baptismal name is Täwäldä Mädḫǝn (s. Additio 3).&#xD;
Gäbrä Mädḫǝn is mentioned in the supplication formulas on fols. 132vb, 156vc, 168rb, 176vc (in the supplication formulas on fol. 126rb, as the commissioner of the book, and on fol. 150vb, along with ʾabunä ʿArʾaya Śǝllase).&#xD;
Other names are added, by a secondary hand, in the unfilled spaces left for rubrication throughout the Ms. and in Additio 2: Gäbrä Yoḥannǝs (fol. 5rc), ʾAbba Kiros (fol. 7va), Täklä ʾAb (fol. 20rb), ʾAmätä Ṣadqan (fols. 50rc, 152rc, 168vb), Gäbrä Mädḥǝn (fol. 89rb) (same as the main text?), Mäzgäbä Śǝllase (fols. 96vb, 162vc), Gäbrä Ṣadqan (fol. 162vc), Täwäldä Mädḫǝn (fols. 118ra, 162vc), Ḫabtä Mikaʾel (118vc), Gäbrä Kidan (fol. 119vc), Wälättä ʾIyäsus (fols. 132vb, 156vc, 157va, 168rb, 176vc), Wälättä Ṣǝyon (fols. 150vb, 162vc, 176vc).</persName>
